translation[13]{c,v,t}:
  21,45,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Chisimu une nguntetela ŵanganyammwe ni maloŵe (ga Allah).” Nambo asiiwa nganaŵa apikene m’bilango, (namuno) achiteteledwaga"
  21,46,"Nambo kalikatite kaakwaye kambungo kaipotesi ya Ambuje ŵenu, chisimu chene mpaka ajile: “Ipotesi yetuwe! Chisimu uwwe twaliji ŵaalitenda lupuso.”"
  21,47,"Ni tuchiŵika masikelo gachilungamiko pa lisiku lya Kiyama, basi mundu jwalijose ngasatendedwa lupuso pachilichose, natamuno (chinducho) chichiŵe chausito wati mpela lupele lwa mbumbi (tanaposi), tuchiika nacho; soni Uwwe tukwanila kuŵa Akuŵalanjila"
  21,48,"Soni chisimu chene Uwwe twampele Musa ni Haruna (Chitabu), chakulekanganya (chilikati cha yakuona ni yaunami, chachaliji) soni lumuli ni chikumbusyo kwa ŵandu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah)"
  21,49,"Aŵala ŵaakun’jogopa M’mbuje gwao mwangali kum’bona, soni ŵanyao Kiyama akasajijogopaga"
  21,50,Sano aji (Qur’an) ni chikumbusyo chaupile chatuchitulwisye; ana jenumanja chalakwechi ni nkuchikana
  21,51,"Soni chisimu chene Uwwe twampele Ibrahima chongoko chakwe kala (kuuchanda), nitwaliji nkummanya chenene"
  21,52,"Pandema jaŵaŵechete kwa babagwe ni ŵandu ŵakwe kuti: “Ana niyapi ayi isanamu yankuŵa jenumanja nchijendelechelaga kuigalagatila?”"
  21,53,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Twasimene achatati ŵetu achiigalagatilaga.”"
  21,54,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Chisimu chene jenumanja ni achatati ŵenu m’bele mukusokonechela kwakuonechela.”"
  21,55,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Ana ntuŵichilile niyakuona kapena n’di mwa akutenda chanache?”"
  21,56,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “(Ngwamba), nambo m’mbuje gwenu ni M’mbuje jwa kumawunde ni petaka Ajula juŵaigumbile yalakweyo, soni une payalakweyo ndili mwa akutendela umboni.”"
  21,57,“Soni ngunnumbila Allah! Chisimu une chindende malindi (gakuijonanga) isanamu yenu panyuma pagalauka ni kulosya migongo jenu (kwaulaga kwakuja kwenu).”